      <title>与合作伙伴的交易结束后，麦当劳在斯里兰卡的门店关闭</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/mcdonalds-stores-close-sri-lanka-after-deal-with-partner-ended-lawyer-says-2024-03-24/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[麦当劳的一名律师周日表示，麦当劳已终止与斯里兰卡当地合作伙伴的协议，该国所有 12 家门店均已关闭。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/mcdonalds-stores-close-sri-lanka-after-deal-with-partner-ended-lawyer-says-2024-03-24/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 24 Mar 2024 13:13:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>恒大清算人称公司、SJ和天际撤回在美国的第15章申请</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/evergrandes-liquidators-say-company-sj-tianji-withdraw-chapter-15-applications-2024-03-24/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[这家中国房地产公司在向香港证券交易所提交的文件中表示，该公司、SJ和天脊集团周五向美国法院提交文件，撤回第15章破产保护申请，该公司清算人表示。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/evergrandes-liquidators-say-company-sj-tianji-withdraw-chapter-15-applications-2024-03-24/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 24 Mar 2024 11:21:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南海事件后中国誓言维护领土完整</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-vows-safeguard-its-territorial-integrity-after-south-china-sea-incident-2024-03-24/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国国防部警告菲律宾不要采取“挑衅”行动，并表示中国将在南海争议海域发生事件的第二天捍卫其领土主权。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-vows-safeguard-its-territorial-integrity-after-south-china-sea-incident-2024-03-24/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 24 Mar 2024 03:19:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚岛州塔斯马尼亚在民意调查后走向少数派政府</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australias-island-state-tasmania-headed-minority-government-after-poll-2024-03-24/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚塔斯马尼亚州周日似乎将组建少数派政府，因为该南部岛州的选举缺乏明显的获胜者，计票仍在继续。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australias-island-state-tasmania-headed-minority-government-after-poll-2024-03-24/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 24 Mar 2024 00:48:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>朝中社称，朝鲜领导人金正恩就大屠杀向普京表示慰问</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/north-korea-leader-kim-jong-un-sends-message-sympathy-putin-over-massacre-kcna-2024-03-23/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[朝中社周日称，朝鲜领导人金正恩就莫斯科音乐厅发生的屠杀事件向俄罗斯总统普京表示慰问，并表示没有任何理由可以为针对人类生命的“令人发指的恐怖主义”辩护。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/north-korea-leader-kim-jong-un-sends-message-sympathy-putin-over-massacre-kcna-2024-03-23/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 23 Mar 2024 21:36:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>GFZ 称巴布亚新几内亚发生里氏 6.7 级地震</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/earthquake-magnitude-69-strikes-papua-new-guinea-gfz-says-2024-03-23/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国地球科学研究中心 (GFZ) 表示，巴布亚新几内亚北部偏远地区周日发生了 6.7 级地震。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/earthquake-magnitude-69-strikes-papua-new-guinea-gfz-says-2024-03-23/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 23 Mar 2024 20:45:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>罗兴亚人船只在亚齐倾覆后，印度尼西亚打捞出两具尸体</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/indonesia-recovers-two-bodies-after-rohingya-boat-capsizes-off-aceh-2024-03-23/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度尼西亚当局周六在西亚齐海岸打捞出两具尸体，并表示当地渔民报告称，一艘载有罗辛亚移民的船只本周早些时候在海岸倾覆后，还有几名溺水者被冲上岸。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/indonesia-recovers-two-bodies-after-rohingya-boat-capsizes-off-aceh-2024-03-23/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 23 Mar 2024 14:44:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>秘鲁“纠正错误”赋予中远集团在大型港口的独家经营权</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/peru-correct-error-that-gave-cosco-exclusivity-megaport-2024-03-23/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[秘鲁港务局表示，希望纠正一个“行政错误”，该错误导致中国中远海运集团获得了新钱凯巨型港口的独家经营权。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/peru-correct-error-that-gave-cosco-exclusivity-megaport-2024-03-23/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 23 Mar 2024 14:23:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印尼总统候选人甘贾尔落选 呼吁重新选举</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/losing-indonesian-presidential-candidate-ganjar-calls-new-election-2024-03-23/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度尼西亚总统候选人甘贾尔·普拉诺沃(Ganjar Pranowo)落选的法律团队周六向该国宪法法院提起诉讼，呼吁重新选举，并取消获胜的国防部长普拉博沃·苏比安托(Prabowo Subianto)团队的资格。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/losing-indonesian-presidential-candidate-ganjar-calls-new-election-2024-03-23/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 23 Mar 2024 12:58:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>故障两天后，联盟号飞船在飞往国际空间站的途中发射升空</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/space/soyuz-craft-launches-en-route-international-space-station-2-days-after-glitch-2024-03-23/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[现场录像显示，周六，一艘载着俄罗斯人、白俄罗斯人和美国人的俄罗斯联盟号飞船从哈萨克斯坦的拜科努尔航天发射场发射升空，前往国际空间站（ISS）。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/technology/space/soyuz-craft-launches-en-route-international-space-station-2-days-after-glitch-2024-03-23/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 23 Mar 2024 12:47:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
